all do me a favor

134
00:06:33,860 --> 00:06:35,760
and just not talk about
this until I tell Pam?

135
00:06:35,828 --> 00:06:36,886
That'd be great.

136
00:06:36,963 --> 00:06:39,591
You haven't told
the missus
about the castle?

137
00:06:39,665 --> 00:06:41,292
You're in
for a spanking,
my friend.

138
00:06:41,367 --> 00:06:43,892
Myself and my lady,
no secrets.

139
00:06:43,970 --> 00:06:45,699
PHYLLIS:
Jim, don't listen to Andy.

140
00:06:45,772 --> 00:06:47,399
