141
00:06:47,473 --> 00:06:48,633
JIM: Oh, thanks, Phyllis.

142
00:06:48,708 --> 00:06:51,108
Bob bought our house without
consulting me and I loved it.

143
00:06:51,177 --> 00:06:52,838
